 337px" data-lazy-src=3D"https://www.statisticssolutions.com/wp-content/upl=
oads/2019/07/wilcoxtable01.jpg"></a></figure>



<p>The next step of the Wilcoxon sign test is to sign each rank.&nbsp; If t=
he original difference &lt; 0 then the rank is multiplied by -1; if the dif=
ference is positive the rank stays positive.</p>



<figure class=3D"wp-block-image"><a href=3D"https://www.statisticssolutions=
