ble03.jpg"></a></figure>



<p>The next step is to calculate the <i>W+ </i>and <i>W-. </i></p>



<p><i>W+</i> =3D 4.5 + 4.5 =3D 9</p>



<p><i>W-</i> =3D 1+ 2 + 4.5 + 4.5 + 7.5 + 7.5 + 9 + 10.5 + 10.5 + 12.5 + 12=
.5 + 14 + 17+ 17 + 17 + 17 + 17 =3D 181</p>



<p>We can double check this knowing&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://www.statisticss=
olutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/n.1.jpg"><img decoding=3D"async" cl=
